<paragraph blockId="84.[189,1399,266,327]" pageId="84" pageNumber="85">WING. Entirely microtrichose; hyaline, stigma yellowish. Crossvein dm-cu meeting vein M slightly obliquely and vein M</paragraph>
<paragraph box="[441,450,320,334]" pageId="84" pageNumber="85">1</paragraph>
